the difference between all three of those,

00:01:50.426 --> 00:01:53.535
and you know what, I think we get all
three but I can't tell the difference.

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:55.118
(Destin) [Laughs] Excellent.

00:01:55.143 --> 00:01:57.416
So if you get a chance,
come up to Baltimore

00:01:57.441 --> 00:01:59.858
and go to the National Electronics Museum.
You'll learn something.

